{"tid":927863,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"無咩事 唔該你唔好若無其事地出現","createTime":"2018-12-04T12:27:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T14:37:53.000Z","uid":216800,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"278815e524b232da45e8b05762a08fab23bb916a","tid":927863,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T12:27:35.000Z","msg":"一粒石仔擊起千重浪 三日都平伏唔到<br />\n你係我初戀 但唔代表你可以若無其事咁出現<br />\n我由a0唔識拍拖到同你一齊 最後到分手<br />\n種種開心回憶點滴在心頭<br />\n由第一次見面<br />\n到唔知點解就一齊左<br />\n中間既開開心心 辛辛酸酸既日子歷歷在目<br />\n最後分手果時既我 事後回顧真係好樣衰<br />\n你知唔知我用左幾耐時間先走得出低谷<br />\n你又知唔知我用左幾多時間先重新接受到其他女仔<br />\n雖然成熟左 雖然理性左<br />\n但你既出現真係會勾起我既情感<br />\n你好討厭⋯⋯<br />\n但又唔可以當住你面叫你唔好再搵我 我做唔出<br />\n以前發誓唔再做地底泥 唔再做隻狗<br />\n依加同做返又有咩分別<br />\n有既...唔會好似以前分左手之後咁lur住你囉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c717048cfd70eab9326ef83f2f4defd82884ff64","tid":927863,"uid":208916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T12:34:06.000Z","msg":"你係咪姓陳架........？"},{"pid":"c1ff2dab4c93878ae4ced217ae94e799d9e456c9","tid":927863,"uid":18569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T12:34:39.000Z","msg":"一次又一次咁傷害我，夠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39dc4115eccb25ce8a5ee231f557a52e9b57114f","tid":927863,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c717048cfd70eab9326ef83f2f4defd82884ff64","tid":927863,"uid":208916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T12:34:06.000Z","msg":"你係咪姓陳架........？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T12:35:49.000Z","msg":"唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做咩"},{"pid":"f021184ad7f1a9a0bfc3d3e24f79935005296021","tid":927863,"uid":208916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39dc4115eccb25ce8a5ee231f557a52e9b57114f","tid":927863,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c717048cfd70eab9326ef83f2f4defd82884ff64","tid":927863,"uid":2089